{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"IntersectionObserverEntry.boundingClientRect","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry/boundingClientRect","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Intersection_Observer_API\">Intersection Observer API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry\"><code>IntersectionObserverEntry</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><em><code>boundingClientRect</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry/intersectionRatio\"><code>intersectionRatio</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry/intersectionRect\"><code>intersectionRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry/isIntersecting\"><code>isIntersecting</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry/rootBounds\"><code>rootBounds</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry/target\"><code>target</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry/time\"><code>time</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Intersection Observer API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserver\"><code>IntersectionObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/indexedDB\"><code>indexedDB</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IntersectionObserverEntry\"><code>IntersectionObserverEntry</code></a> interface's read-only\n  <strong><code>boundingClientRect</code></strong> property returns a\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRectReadOnly\"><code>DOMRectReadOnly</code></a> which in essence describes a re